        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6373",
        "content": "Indeed, I had so well secured them in their places, that such an accident was entirely out of the question. Looking at my watch, I found it six o'clock.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
