        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6373",
        "content": "Immediately beneath me in the ocean, lay a small black object, slightly oblong in shape, seemingly about the size, and in every way bearing a great resemblance to one of those childish toys called a domino.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
